    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this absolute gem! It\u2019s in seriously incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re gonna love it! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
