    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been curated with exhaustive attention to detail and rigorous mechanical preservation. Every surface reflects a standard of care synonymous with factory-fresh delivery. We invite the most discerning buyers to experience a level of excellence that transcends the typical pre-owned market.",
      "price": 44900.0,
