      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s in absolute mint condition and honestly looks like it just rolled out of the showroom! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, keeping it garage-parked and spotless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and still has that 'new car' feel that's so hard to find. I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale, so come grab this gem before someone else beats you to it! Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive today!",
      "price": 43900.0,
