      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six and a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis has been inspected and reinforced at the subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional power delivery out of corners, while the factory-spec suspension maintains original damping rates. Finished in a mirror-like Carbon Black, the exterior exhibits zero clear coat failure or panel misalignment. This is a collector-grade vehicle with a crisp throttle response and a high-revving power band that remains as sharp as the day it left Regensburg.",
